title: Cais do Porto do Moniz
body: It was built by the Junta Geral in 1916. Before that, there was a natural landing place in Porto do Moniz, and later a staircase was built by the same corporation for the embarkation and disembarkation of passengers at high tide.

Porto do Moniz: Before the construction of the pier, there was a natural landing place.

1916: Construction of the pier at Porto do Moniz.
